1
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:30,400
Mr. Jiang.

2
00:01:31,720 --> 00:01:32,960
Sign it,

3
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:36,680
and I'll make sure your position
at Lu Group is secure.

4
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:41,120
My dad is already old.

5
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,479
Fan, you are still young.

6
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:47,610
The Lu Group will be yours
sooner or later.

7
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,920
Why the rush?

8
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:51,759
Besides, Chairman Lu treats me well.

9
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,680
I won't betray him.

10
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:59,570
You need to know
which way the wind's blowing.

11
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,600
There isn't that much friendship
in business.

12
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,600
They...

13
00:02:13,320 --> 00:02:14,120
They...

14
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:19,120
Don't think I'm the same as them!

15
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,680
You want to take control of the Lu Group.

16
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:23,440
Win the Zhongyu bid,

17
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:24,560
and you'll have

18
00:02:24,600 --> 00:02:26,200
my full support from then on.

19
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:33,250
Don't worry. Have a seat first.

20
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:34,400
Sit.

21
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,160
You.

22
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:49,720
Good.

23
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,720
Very good.

24
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,240
Good for you.

25
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,480
Thank you, Mr. Jiang.

26
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:06,360
The board wants to remove me.

27
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:08,200
You're behind this.

28
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,480
From today on,

29
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:13,090
I will take full charge
of the company's affairs.

30
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:14,080
Seizing power?

31
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,000
Good.

32
00:03:22,840 --> 00:03:23,560
Lu Fan,

33
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,600
I am your father!

34
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,340
It's because you are my father

35
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:29,640
that I'm giving you this chance.

36
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:34,160
Cancel today's wedding.

37
00:03:36,640 --> 00:03:37,440
Cancel it?

38
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,920
You can't just call it off.

39
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:41,880
What about the Lu family's reputation?

40
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:43,000
It's your wedding.

41
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,320
How you deal with it is up to you.

42
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,450
I won't do it for you.

43
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:47,800
Mr. Lu,

44
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:51,250
there's a problem
with the Zhongyu Group's bidding.

45
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,690
It's been ten years.

46
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:56,000
This is the price you're paying
for my mother's death.

47
00:03:56,079 --> 00:03:57,840
If you don't cherish this opportunity,

48
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,720
think about

49
00:03:59,880 --> 00:04:01,810
what else you have left to pay with.

50
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,130
Are you threatening me?

51
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:07,600
It's not a threat.

52
00:04:09,040 --> 00:04:10,570
It's just letting you know.

53
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,520
Xia.

54
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,800
The wedding is about to begin.

55
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,080
Are you ready?

56
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:49,520
Ready for what?

57
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:51,960
To watch you put on

58
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,240
a show of sisterly love?

59
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,280
Xia.

60
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:04,200
There were things
I couldn't tell you before.

61
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,560
But now you need to understand—

62
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,920
I never did any of this

63
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,840
for myself,

64
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,960
and certainly not for wealth or status.

65
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,640
It's to end it,

66
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:18,320
once and for all.

67
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,800
I will finish this in my own way.

68
00:05:22,960 --> 00:05:23,960
Remember.

69
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:26,840
No matter what happens today,

70
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,160
no matter what you hear,

71
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,520
protect yourself well

72
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,450
and stay far away from here.

73
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,680
Enough, Su Dong.

74
00:05:36,159 --> 00:05:37,720
Stop your hypocrisy.

75
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:39,560
You are about to wear this dress,

76
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,640
go out to accept everyone's blessings,

77
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:43,560
and become the glamorous Mrs. Lu.

78
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:45,760
Finish it?

79
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:49,740
What a great excuse.
What a noble sacrifice.

80
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:50,760
It's just

81
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:52,640
a fig leaf for your vanity.

82
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,480
What you can't bear
to let go of is this immense wealth

83
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,920
and your title as Mrs. Lu.

84
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,360
Do you even realize

85
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,360
everything you have has come

86
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,320
at the cost of Dad's life?

87
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,250
And you still want me

88
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:06,140
to understand and thank you
from the bottom of my heart?

89
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:08,240
I don't need your instructions.

90
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:15,480
Look at your expression.

91
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:18,600
It's just like the wedding dress on you,

92
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:21,440
making me feel they
are both cheap and disgusting.

93
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:23,640
Since you've chosen to marry your enemy

94
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:25,840
and keep living your life of luxury,

95
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:28,080
I will walk my own path.

96
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:30,640
I don't need your hypocritical advice.

97
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,280
Have a happy marriage.

98
00:06:48,960 --> 00:06:49,600
Welcome.

99
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,820
Congratulations.

100
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,360
Thank you.

101
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,340
Please come in.

102
00:06:56,320 --> 00:06:57,159
Mr. Zhang.

103
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:58,520
Thank you, Mr. Zhang.

104
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,000
Thank you.

105
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:31,700
It seems Lu Fan will
make a move before you do.

106
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,600
The result he wants

107
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,840
is different from what I want.

108
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,940
Looking forward to it.

109
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,560
Quiet, everyone.

110
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:53,880
I'd like to introduce someone special.

111
00:07:54,520 --> 00:07:56,080
This is Ms. Liang.

112
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,400
She has taken care of the Lu family
for 20 years

113
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,730
and is like family to us.

114
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:00,880
Today, she

115
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:03,640
has specially prepared a piano piece
for our wedding

116
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,760
as a gift.

117
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:30,840
Xia.

118
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,000
It's fake.

119
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,919
Everyone.

120
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,320
It's fake!

121
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:46,400
What you are seeing must be fake.

122
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:47,480
You know,

123
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:49,640
this photo has been doctored.

124
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,300
Someone is trying to frame me.

125
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,720
Dong,

126
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,440
explain it to everyone.

127
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,120
Explain it clearly.

128
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:58,720
Tell them it's fake.

129
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,240
Say something!

130
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,440
Everyone,

131
00:09:09,160 --> 00:09:11,840
I, Lu Zhen'an, have let you all down.

132
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,280
Su Dong and I

133
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,520
have been in love for many years.

134
00:09:18,280 --> 00:09:20,480
My brother
entrusted these two sisters

135
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,680
to me.

136
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,960
I know her character.

137
00:09:24,280 --> 00:09:25,400
She is not that kind of person.

138
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:28,440
Otherwise, we wouldn't have
been together for so long.

139
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,720
Please rest assured.

140
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:33,800
Someone fabricated all of this

141
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:36,000
to frame me!

142
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,220
The wedding will go on.

143
00:09:41,560 --> 00:09:43,040
Sorry for spoiling the mood.

144
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:43,680
Emcee.

145
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:51,520
Xia.

146
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,840
Hello, dear guests.

147
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:02,740
I am Su Xia, Ms. Su Dong's younger sister.

148
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:05,800
Today, on this joyous day,

149
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:08,240
I'd like to offer

150
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,570
my heartfelt blessings

151
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:12,200
to my adoptive father and my sister.

152
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:14,640
Brother.

153
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:16,840
Do you love me?

154
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:18,680
Yes, I do.

155
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,580
What about you?

156
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,880
Mr. Lu, what exactly is the relationship

157
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:45,040
between you and your sister, Su Xia?

158
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:46,040
If you had known your father

159
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,680
would marry her sister,

160
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,720
would you still be with her?

161
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,240
Would you still sleep with her, Mr. Lu?

162
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:50,840
Mr. Lu!

163
00:10:50,840 --> 00:10:51,960
Please answer.

164
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,720
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

165
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,120
Mr. Lu, say a few words.

166
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,980
Mr. Lu, say a few words, Mr. Lu!

167
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:58,880
Mr. Lu, say a few words.

168
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,240
Mr. Lu, please say a few words.

169
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:02,400
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

170
00:11:03,680 --> 00:11:04,880
Mr. Lu Zhen'an.

171
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,160
Ms. Su Dong.

172
00:11:06,920 --> 00:11:09,480
Do you take each other in marriage,

173
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,880
to love, honor,

174
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:13,320
and cherish one another,

175
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,480
in sickness

176
00:11:14,880 --> 00:11:16,040
and in health,

177
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:18,060
for as long as you both shall live?

178
00:11:19,040 --> 00:11:19,800
You...

179
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,000
Su Xia.

180
00:11:21,960 --> 00:11:24,220
If you've got a problem,
take it out on me.

181
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:26,640
Why do you hurt yourself like this?

182
00:11:27,600 --> 00:11:28,320
Su Xia.

183
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:32,680
Why did you do this?

184
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:33,760
Brother,

185
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,280
you're here.

186
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,840
Why?

187
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:40,420
Because everyone
in the Lu family is guilty.

188
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:41,570
My medicine.

189
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:03,060
Ladies and gentlemen,

190
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:09,520
today I'd like you to listen
to a few short stories.

191
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:12,840
Su Dong, what are you trying to say?

192
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,480
The first story

193
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,600
is about a patent—

194
00:12:20,480 --> 00:12:25,140
High-Efficiency Lithium-Ion Battery
Anode Material Manufacturing Technology.

195
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:28,880
Its inventor was Su Minghao.

196
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:31,220
He was my father...

197
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,640
and Su Xia's.

198
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,400
Shut up!

199
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:36,800
It's him.

200
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:38,920
Lu Zhen'an.

201
00:12:40,200 --> 00:12:41,600
You were blinded by greed

202
00:12:42,160 --> 00:12:44,040
and drove our father to his death.

203
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:47,920
The data must be changed

204
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:51,120
right before Su Minghao
submits the final report.

205
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,050
The parameters.

206
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:55,080
Right, the key stability parameters.

207
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:58,760
That's a shameless forgery!

208
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:01,240
Lu Zhen'an, calm down.

209
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,880
The show has just begun.

210
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:06,000
The bank is taken care of.

211
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,160
The bank will call in the loan
the day the test fails.

212
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:10,120
The press headline we've prepared is:

213
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:13,040
Genius Engineer Su Minghao
Exposed for Fraud

214
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,840
as Billion-Yuan Project Collapses.
